Re: Does this make sense?
by Cyborg Ninja » Thu 06.16.2011 3:50 pm That was a big help, thank you. I really need to work on counters - I totally forget to use them. I will work on more natural sentence construction, too.By the way, I'm impressed you know that the period goes before the closing quotation mark in English. Not even many native English speakers know that.
